universe and gives her courage.

00:23:22.060 --> 00:23:25.911
Tell me what it is about this
role that appealed to you

00:23:25.911 --> 00:23:26.994
because it seemed natural.

00:23:26.994 --> 00:23:29.240
OPRAH WINFREY: I have to
say, well, first of all,

00:23:29.240 --> 00:23:32.140
let me just say that one of
the reasons this role happened

00:23:32.140 --> 00:23:35.290
