she was prepared.

00:40:35.100 --> 00:40:38.445
Luck is just preparation meeting
that moment of opportunity.

00:40:38.445 --> 00:40:41.140
If she wasn't prepared,
she wouldn't be here.

00:40:41.140 --> 00:40:45.480
So your job is to fill
yourself with as much light.

00:40:45.480 --> 00:40:47.760
Light comes from
all that is good,

00:40:47.760 --> 00:40:51.270
all that is grace, all that
is kindness, and then offer

00:40:51.270 --> 00:40:52.770
